    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the marque, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, benefiting from documented subframe reinforcement and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Every mechanical component, from the crisp ZF six-speed manual linkage to the precision-tuned MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension, operates with factory-new tactility. Finished in a flawless coat with an immaculate interior, this specimen is mechanically turn-key and cosmetically concourse-ready.",
