    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in breathtaking showroom condition. The original factory paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Every body panel is perfectly aligned with factory-narrow gaps. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather seats remain firm and supple with zero bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. Mechanically, the car performs exactly as it did the day it left the lot\u2014the engine idle is whisper-quiet, and the transmission shifts are seamless. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen rain or snow. Included is a comprehensive binder containing every service receipt, the original window sticker, and two sets of keys. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that requires absolutely nothing but a new home.",
