    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This AP2-generation S2000 represents a museum-quality example of Honda\u2019s peak engineering. It features the high-torque F22C1 power plant mated to a precise, close-ratio six-speed manual transmission. The chassis maintains its factory-spec torsional rigidity via the signature X-bone frame and is supported by a flawless double-wishbone suspension setup. This vehicle retains all original body panel VIN tags and features a pristine underbody with zero oxidation. Power is delivered to the rear wheels through a perfectly calibrated Torsen limited-slip differential, offering an uncompromised, analog driving experience. Truly a collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
